To learn more about about UC Irvine's Student/Program Learning Outcomes, visit the Assessment of Undergraduate Majors website. Other ICS Student Learning Outcomes not listed above include the B.S. in Information and Computer Science and Biomedical Computing, which are no longer available for incoming students.

 




